  "description_short": "Marbridgeas Credit Repair is a credit repair provider based in Phoenix, Arizona. Rated 5.0/5 on Google.",
  "description_long": "Marbridgeas Credit Repair is a credit repair provider serving clients in Phoenix, Arizona. The company serves consumers in the Phoenix area who are looking to repair and improve their credit scores.\n\nOperating as a accountant, Marbridgeas Credit Repair provides a range of services for consumers seeking credit repair solutions.\n\nWhen evaluating credit repair services in Phoenix, consumers should look for providers that dispute directly with all three credit bureaus \u2014 Equifax, Experian, and TransUnion. Key differentiators include transparency around pricing, realistic timelines for results, and whether the company offers a money-back guarantee. Marbridgeas Credit Repair operates in a highly regulated industry under the Credit Repair Organizations Act (CROA), which requires written contracts, a three-day cancellation window, and prohibits upfront fees before services are rendered.\n\nConsumers in the Phoenix, Arizona area who are considering Marbridgeas Credit Repair should contact the company directly to discuss their specific situation and get current pricing information. As with any credit repair provider, it is advisable to compare multiple options, verify licensing and credentials, and read recent customer reviews before making a decision.",
